          "source_object_fileID": 226737633,
          "condition": "Level2.unity -> GameObject 'Elevator' has a BoxCollider (isTrigger=1) and no Rigidbody. It has MonoBehaviour (component fileID 4942415221793979109) using script guid 077cb2d6a53b18f4ea7d76e72138fc77 (AttachToElevator). The 'player' field is null in scene. To cover OnTriggerEnter, simulate a collider (intended player) entering the Elevator's trigger. Note: script compares gameObject == player instead of other.gameObject == player, so even with a correct player reference, parenting will not occur. No m_Calls events are defined.",
          "triggerring_events": [
